imdb.plot outline: Count down to the New Year with Taiwan's biggest event of the year! The "2014 Taipei 101 New Year's Eve Countdown" promises to be the must-see event of the year, with past years' events being named by CNN as among the "Top 10 Countries With the Most Unique Countdowns" and drawing thousands of spectators to Taipei's beautiful 101 Building, which is 509 meters high.
